      <title>欧盟考虑限制俄罗斯农产品进口</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/eu-mulls-restrictions-on-imports-of-russian-agriculture-products</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在一些希望向克里姆林宫施加进一步压力的成员国发出呼吁后，欧盟执委会正在准备一项限制从俄罗斯进口农产品的提案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/eu-mulls-restrictions-on-imports-of-russian-agriculture-products</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 15:21:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>七国集团盟国警告伊朗不要向俄罗斯供应导弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/g-7-allies-warn-iran-against-supplying-russia-with-missiles</link>
      <description><![CDATA[七国集团警告伊朗不要向俄罗斯提供弹道导弹用于乌克兰战争，并威胁称如果伊朗这样做，伊朗将迅速做出反应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/g-7-allies-warn-iran-against-supplying-russia-with-missiles</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 15:15:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>魁北克利用金融战争基金来缓解赤字增加的成本</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/quebec-taps-financial-war-chest-to-ease-cost-of-higher-deficits</link>
      <description><![CDATA[魁北克省财政部长公布的预算文件预计未来几年的赤字将大幅增加，因此魁北克省计划从应急基金中提取数十亿加元，以减少借贷需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/quebec-taps-financial-war-chest-to-ease-cost-of-higher-deficits</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 15:07:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>健康保险公司与美国就网络攻击后的救济问题产生分歧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/health-insurers-split-with-us-over-relief-after-change-healthcare-hack</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于上个月的网络攻击继续阻碍数十亿美元的付款，医疗保险公司和美国政府官员预计将于下周举行会议，讨论如何协助现金短缺的医疗机构的分歧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/health-insurers-split-with-us-over-relief-after-change-healthcare-hack</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 15:03:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哥伦比亚央行行长表示数据为更大幅度降息铺平道路</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/colombia-central-banker-says-data-paves-way-for-bigger-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哥伦比亚央行董事会成员表示，哥伦比亚通胀放缓和经济疲软需要更大幅度的降息，但政策制定者必须对未来的潜在风险保持警惕。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/colombia-central-banker-says-data-paves-way-for-bigger-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 14:54:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普审判延迟增加了起诉流产的可能性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/trump-trial-delays-raise-the-prospect-of-aborted-prosecutions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普封口费案的审判可能会被推迟，这是检察官在 11 月之前审理他的其他刑事案件的努力的最新复杂化，这增加了这位共和党总统候选人当选的可能性——也许就职——在对他提出最严重的指控之前]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/trump-trial-delays-raise-the-prospect-of-aborted-prosecutions</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 14:42:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贸易紧张局势持续，马克龙将在巴黎接待中国习近平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/macron-to-host-china-s-xi-in-paris-as-trade-tensions-persist</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于欧盟与世界第二大经济体之间的贸易紧张局势持续存在，法国总统马克龙计划于春季在巴黎接待中国国家主席习近平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/macron-to-host-china-s-xi-in-paris-as-trade-tensions-persist</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 14:31:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法官裁定，如果首席检察官离职，威利斯可以继续审理特朗普佐治亚州案件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/trump-prosecutor-fani-willis-can-stay-on-georgia-election-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法官裁定，只要与富尔顿县地方检察官法妮·威利斯有恋爱关系的首席检察官内森·韦德下台，富尔顿县地方检察官法妮·威利斯就可以继续监督佐治亚州唐纳德·特朗普的选举干预案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/trump-prosecutor-fani-willis-can-stay-on-georgia-election-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 13:08:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列在恢复停火谈判的同时准备袭击拉法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/israel-prepares-rafah-evacuation-after-netanyahu-approves-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在平民被撤离后，以色列战时内阁批准对加沙城市拉法发动袭击，这表明当局准备在停火谈判正在进行的情况下加大对哈马斯的打击力度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/israel-prepares-rafah-evacuation-after-netanyahu-approves-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 12:57:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管人口外流速度放缓，纽约市仍失去了 546,000 名居民</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/nyc-has-lost-546-000-residents-since-covid-even-as-exodus-slows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国人口普查数据显示，尽管自疫情大流行以来人口外流速度放缓，但纽约市去年失去了近 78,000 名居民，使自 2020 年 4 月以来总减少人数超过 50 万。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/nyc-has-lost-546-000-residents-since-covid-even-as-exodus-slows</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 15:14:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
